<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>AirPods Max</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/index.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="navbar">
    <div class="logo">
      <img style="height: 60px;" src="./img/memory_umbrella_logo.png" alt="">
    </div>
    <nav>
      <a href="#">Products</a>
      <a href="#">Prices</a>
      <a href="./download">Overview</a>
      <a href="#">Contacts</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <!-- Sección 1 -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="text">
      <h1>Air<br>Pods<br>Max</h1>
      <p>“AirPods are the most popular headphones in the world, beloved for their effortless setup, incredible sound quality, and iconic design.”</p>
      <button>Read More</button>
    </div>
    <div class="image">
      <img src="./img/memory_umbrella_open.png" alt="AirPods Max">
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sección 2 -->
  <section class="feature">
    <div class="image">
      <img src="./img/memory_umbrella_case.png" alt="AirPods Max uso">
    </div>
    <div class="text">
      <h2>Sounds like<br>an epiphany</h2>
      <p>Industry-leading Active Noise Cancellation counters external sound with equal anti-noise, allowing you to immerse yourself in what you’re listening to.</p>
      <p>Press the noise control button to switch to Transparency mode, which lets outside sound in so you can interact naturally with your surroundings.</p>
      <div class="arrow">➜</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sección 3 -->
  <section class="feature reverse">
    <div class="text">
      <h2>Magical<br>experience</h2>
      <p>AirPods Max inherit all of the wireless, effortless magic of the AirPods family. From setup to Siri commands, they make the listening experience completely fluid — day to day, device to device.</p>
      <button>Read More</button>
    </div>
    <div class="image">
      <img src="./img/memory_umbrella_open_1.png" alt="AirPods Max case">
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
